data.description:
Seller to Entertain or Counter Offers between $200,000-$225,000. Are you ready for a lifestyle change? Need a little more space? Then come visit this charming home featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 baths with an open floor plan. This Manufactured home is 1,216 SqFt and was built in 1998. Located in Tucson's Extended West on almost an Acre with natural desert landscape, no HOA & endless possibilities. The private driveway leads to the home with plenty of room for parking and entertaining. Step into the living room with ceiling fan that flows into the functional kitchen with high quality cabinets, LP gas range and dishwasher. There are plenty of windows for natural light and panoramic views. The generously sized Owners bedroom features a large ensuite and walk-in closet. Through the double doors, you'll appreciate the size of the primary bath with shower/tub & dual vanity with cabinets and storage shelving.

This home is a split floor plan with two bedrooms and bathroom with shower/tub on the opposite end of the home. You will enjoy this home as it exudes peace and privacy in the heart of the desert. Unlimited outdoor space with established trees and cactus. Enjoy calming mountain views with panoramic sunrises & sunsets. There is a fabulous  20x20 workshop next to the house. Bring all your toys, such as RV, ATV, and boat. There is plenty of space! And remember no HOA restrictions. The property is fully fenced and there is the possibility for a horse property.

Relaxing indoor/outdoor living at its finest... Make the call to see this today!
